        "type": "nodetool.text.Prompt",
        "data": {
          "prompt": "Art direction:\n{{ direction }}\n\nBase style: {{ style }}\n\nTask: write exactly {{ count }} distinct text-to-image prompts for concept-art variations. Every prompt must obey the art direction and base style above so the set reads as one coherent gallery.\n\nEach prompt must:\n- Keep the same subject and core concept\n- Explore a different composition, pose, or camera angle\n- Name explicit lighting, color, and atmosphere\n- Be one dense sentence tuned for an image model\n\nOutput format: one prompt per line, exactly {{ count }} lines. No numbering, bullets, quotes, or blank lines.",
          "dynamic_properties": {
            "direction": "",
            "style": "Painterly digital concept art, dramatic cinematic lighting, rich saturated color, visible brushwork, AAA game key art",
            "count": 4
          }
